Class BRNode

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IFXGNode, IPreserveWhiteSpaceNode, ITextNode

    public class BRNode
extends AbstractRichTextLeafNode
    Represents a <br /> child tag of FXG <RichText> content. A <br /> tag acts as a line separator for text content.

    This is an empty tag - text content or child tags are not expected.
